{"tid":2115852,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實曼聯得罪你地啲咩...","createTime":"2020-07-19T19:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T19:19:55.000Z","uid":146934,"like":11,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cb4040c2bb64c16598d7f02d42b49ae1a486a1bb","tid":2115852,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T19:07:02.000Z","msg":"費南迪斯爆蛋<br />\n拜利爆頭爆到入廠 而家生死未卜<br />\n你地班車狗都可以係到笑 <br />\n到底有冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日笑鳩迪基亞世一廢龍<br />\n好好笑咩 唔覺囉sorry<br />\n一個人喺低谷嘅時候應該要鼓勵而唔係更多嘅責罵<br />\n<br />\n想像下<br />\n你班車狗死老母嗰陣 我喺你隔離笑鳩你<br />\n仲話你老母係雞 你會唔會覺得難過？ <br />\n<br />\n一句講哂 曼聯係拎過13次英超冠軍的偉大球隊<br />\n希望再講空難聯/獌狗的人會遭受皇天擊殺<br />\n以我皇者獌之名發誓<br />\n請respect 謝謝🙏🏿"},{"pid":"3cc31fd3baae85a425a946387f3d0dc188644c23","tid":2115852,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T19:08:11.000Z","msg":"講叫雖敗猶榮，君子報仇 十年不晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e940d5f405705a3b93d7c8924488f1853dd39c","tid":2115852,"uid":181706,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T19:08:12.000Z","msg":"4424"},{"pid":"d3ac36288bca545c99f565905d88db62716bb182","tid":2115852,"uid":124292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T19:09:05.000Z","msg":"車狗正仆街，希望黎多次慕尼黑空難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b7cd67a52aae9e76a50dbfd2e65d9fbfd39a55","tid":2115852,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T19:09:22.000Z","msg":"三分耳袋打後先睇波？"},{"pid":"0d506126604d41e51ae517e3ef19cb5084ddf6d8","tid":2115852,"uid":320273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T19:10:50.000Z","msg":"我一路難過一路不由自主咁喺度笑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa68cdb19c1eff6fd3ed1ea27430